:null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/05ec/cc96/454161_mini.png?m=1643083246","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/05ec/cc96/454161_normal.png?m=1643083246","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/05ec/cc96/454161_large.png?m=1643083246","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/05ec/cc96/454161_xlarge.png?m=1643083246","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/05ec/cc96/454161_xlarge.png?m=1643083246","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/05ec/cc96/454161_xlarge.png?m=1643083246","created":1574167622,"last_modified":1643083246},"last_reply_by":"zachgenius","last_touched":1666067068,"title":"数字永生 meternal 项目寻全栈联创！","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/887714","created":1666060773,"deleted":0,"content":"有品位的全栈在哪里！\r\n\r\n新项目数字永生人 meternal 初创团队寻有品位的全栈工程师，理念相投可以给股份担任 CTO ，团队来自中科院北大北影巴黎高师，有兴趣留言或者加微信联系：MTUwMTExMDg5NDA=","content_rendered":"有品位的全栈在哪里！<br /><br />新项目数字永生人 meternal 初创团队寻有品位的全栈工程师，理念相投可以给股份担任 CTO ，团队来自中科院北大北影巴黎高师，有兴趣留言或者加微信联系：MTUwMTExMDg5NDA=","last_modified":1666060773,"replies":15,"id":887714},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_large.png?m=1651565926","name":"linux","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_normal.png?m=1651565926","title":"Linux","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","topics":6979,"footer":"","header":"Linux is a Unix-like computer operating system assembled under the model of free and open source software development and distribution.","title_alternative":"Linux","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1651565926","stars":5931,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":11,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":543590,"username":"LxnChan","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/LxnChan","website":"https://lxnchan.cn/?from=v2ex","twitter":"LingXuanNing","psn":"","github":"lxnchan","btc":"","location":"天津","tagline":"","bio":"Source Of Heart Beating.","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c27d945d034f2da687304f5ec6dab8ec?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c27d945d034f2da687304f5ec6dab8ec?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c27d945d034f2da687304f5ec6dab8ec?s=73&d=retro","created":1619283454,"last_modified":1652359190},"last_reply_by":"zerone0086","last_touched":1666067832,"title":"CentOS7 需要在开机时执行一个一次性脚本，请问如何操作？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/887703","created":1666060029,"deleted":0,"content":"现有一个一次性脚本，需要在开机时以**特定用户和组**执行（执行后该脚本相当于以后台守护的方式执行）。\r\n\r\n现在有以下几种方案：\r\n\r\n1. `rc.local`：写进去是写进去了但是不知道为什么死活不生效。\r\n2. SystemD：创建了 Service 配置文件，但是会报错，也没有正确启动。\r\n\r\n目前已经确认的是`rc.local`已经加了对应的权限：\r\n\r\n```sh\r\n[root@testbench-C ~]# ll /etc/rc.local\r\nlrwxrwxrwx. 1 root root 13 Sep 18 23:46 /etc/rc.local -> rc.d/rc.local\r\n[root@testbench-C ~]# ll /etc/rc.d/rc.local\r\n-rwxr--r--. 1 root root 542 Oct 17 22:04 /etc/rc.d/rc.local\r\n```\r\n\r\nSystemD 配置文件：\r\n\r\n```conf\r\n[Unit]\r\nDescription=myservice\r\nAfter=syslog.target\r\nAfter=network.target\r\n\r\n[Service]\r\nType=oneshot\r\nUser=myuser\r\nGroup=myuser\r\nExecStart=/home/tsh2/my.sh start\r\n\r\n[Install]\r\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\r\n```","content_rendered":"<p>现有一个一次性脚本，需要在开机时以<strong>特定用户和组</strong>执行（执行后该脚本相当于以后台守护的方式执行）。</p>\n<p>现在有以下几种方案：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>rc.local</code>：写进去是写进去了但是不知道为什么死活不生效。</li>\n<li>SystemD：创建了 Service 配置文件，但是会报错，也没有正确启动。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>目前已经确认的是<code>rc.local</code>已经加了对应的权限：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-sh\">[root@testbench-C ~]# ll /etc/rc.local\nlrwxrwxrwx. 1 root root 13 Sep 18 23:46 /etc/rc.local -&gt; rc.d/rc.local\n[root@testbench-C ~]# ll /etc/rc.d/rc.local\n-rwxr--r--. 1 root root 542 Oct 17 22:04 /etc/rc.d/rc.local\n</code></pre>\n<p>SystemD 配置文件：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-conf\">[Unit]\nDescription=myservice\nAfter=syslog.target\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=oneshot\nUser=myuser\nGroup=myuser\nExecStart=/home/tsh2/my.sh start\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\n</code></pre>\n","last_modified":1666060085,"replies":15,"id":887703},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":191470,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3586,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":478802,"username":"xiaoliu926","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xiaoliu926","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/93bd/3fa6/478802_mini.png?m=1607570665","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/93bd/3fa6/478802_normal.png?m=1607570665","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/93bd/3fa6/478802_large.png?m=1607570665","created":1585123845,"last_modified":1607570665},"last_reply_by":"ztxcccc","last_touched":1666067961,"title":"现在上海垃圾分类是怎么了？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/887732","created":1666063131,"deleted":0,"content":"现在马路上的垃圾桶越来越少了，大家是怎么处理垃圾的？比如饮料瓶，废纸巾","content_rendered":"<p>现在马路上的垃圾桶越来越少了，大家是怎么处理垃圾的？比如饮料瓶，废纸巾</p>\n","last_modified":1666063131,"replies":14,"id":887732},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":20189,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2359,"aliases":[