//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3d7ab22754811b598ff994b836a1f55?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3d7ab22754811b598ff994b836a1f55?s=73&d=retro","created":1504943441,"last_modified":1504943441},"last_reply_by":"morty0","last_touched":1666066839,"title":"有感而发，快捷指令能做到吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/887738","created":1666064136,"deleted":0,"content":"平常耳机盒经常忘记充电，用光了电量，没有电量方面的提示，快捷指令能不能做到，耳机盒连上手机的时候触发下指令，判断耳机盒低电量给个消息提示。","content_rendered":"<p>平常耳机盒经常忘记充电，用光了电量，没有电量方面的提示，快捷指令能不能做到，耳机盒连上手机的时候触发下指令，判断耳机盒低电量给个消息提示。</p>\n","last_modified":1666064136,"replies":8,"id":887738},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1635654723","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1635654723","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":11586,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723","stars":5933,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"id":590960,"username":"Jimmyisme","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Jimmyisme","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3a6486c13ab675efb4c685136ba288e?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3a6486c13ab675efb4c685136ba288e?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a3a6486c13ab675efb4c685136ba288e?s=73&d=retro","created":1660210586,"last_modified":1666062265},"last_reply_by":"Jimmyisme","last_touched":1666065906,"title":"如何部署完全 ipv6 的代理？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/887731","created":1666062989,"deleted":0,"content":"## 需求\r\n\r\n因为学校的校园网用 ipv6 可以免流量。然后家里正好有一台服务器，1000M 下行 150M 上行且支持 ipv6 。\r\n\r\n![网速]( https://img.tujidu.com/images/2022/10/18/634e1ae8cce70.png)\r\n\r\n## 现在有的东西\r\n\r\n1. 家里用的是华为 AX3Pro 作主路由，AX3Pro 上面可以直接用贝锐的域名做公网 ipv4 的 ddns 。\r\n2. TrueNas 上的 openwrt 虚拟机（配置了 openclash 做透明代理）\r\n\r\n## 目前的想法\r\n\r\n先让 openwrt 获取到公网 ipv6 ，再重新搭建一套纯 ipv6 的代理。\r\n\r\n## 有几个小问题。\r\n\r\n1. openwrt 获取不到任何 ipv6 地址。但是 OpenClash 上是可以正常代理 ipv6 的流量的。（如果这个无法解决的话，TrueNas 是有公网 ipv6 的。有没有其他曲线救国的方案？）\r\n![接口]( https://img.tujidu.com/image/634e199d6f289.jpg)\r\n\r\n2. 有没有一种代理可以达到：学校->家（用 ipv6 通信），家->公网（用 ipv4+ipv6 通信）。","content_rendered":"<h2>需求</h2>\n<p>因为学校的校园网用 ipv6 可以免流量。然后家里正好有一台服务器，1000M 下行 150M 上行且支持 ipv6 。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"网速\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://img.tujidu.com/images/2022/10/18/634e1ae8cce70.png\"/></p>\n<h2>现在有的东西</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>家里用的是华为 AX3Pro 作主路由，AX3Pro 上面可以直接用贝锐的域名做公网 ipv4 的 ddns 。</li>\n<li>TrueNas 上的 openwrt 虚拟机（配置了 openclash 做透明代理）</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>目前的想法</h2>\n<p>先让 openwrt 获取到公网 ipv6 ，再重新搭建一套纯 ipv6 的代理。</p>\n<h2>有几个小问题。</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>openwrt 获取不到任何 ipv6 地址。但是 OpenClash 上是可以正常代理 ipv6 的流量的。（如果这个无法解决的话，TrueNas 是有公网 ipv6 的。有没有其他曲线救国的方案？）\n<img alt=\"接口\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://img.tujidu.com/image/634e199d6f289.jpg\"/></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>有没有一种代理可以达到：学校-&gt;家（用 ipv6 通信），家-&gt;公网（用 ipv4+ipv6 通信）。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","last_modified":1666063157,"replies":8,"id":887731},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":191470,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3586,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":529091,"username":"zznext","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zznext","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":nu